Being a bestselling writer isn't easy,
I tell you. Here it is, here it is.

18
00:01:54,347 --> 00:01:55,871
What? It's open.

19
00:01:56,483 --> 00:01:57,817
Hello!

20
00:01:57,817 --> 00:02:00,217
My goodness, just look at that mess.

21
00:02:00,453 --> 00:02:01,977
Keep it a little neater.

22
00:02:03,423 --> 00:02:05,024
Blood!

23
00:02:05,024 --> 00:02:05,991
What?!

24
00:02:06,993 --> 00:02:08,790
It leads into that room.

25
00:02:18,338 --> 00:02:23,298
A Mischievous Mokkori Detective?!
A Beautiful Writer's Mystery Game

26
00:02:23,877 --> 00:02:25,606
Ryo, we have to notify the police.

27
00:02:26,112 --> 00:02:28,706
The perpetrator may still be
lurking somewhere.

28
