Just possibly, I can revive her
with artificial respiration.

35
00:02:59,913 --> 00:03:04,213
In other words, mouth-to-mouth respiration!

36
00:03:11,891 --> 00:03:13,193
How did you know?!

37
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:15,695
Telling the difference between
ink and blood is simple!

38
00:03:15,695 --> 00:03:17,788
Forget that. Let's consummate
our love instead.

39
00:03:18,164 --> 00:03:19,132
Liar

40
